IO-Prompt-Hooked

Simple prompting with validation hooks.

DESCRIPTION

Simple, portable prompts, similar to IO::Prompt::Tiny, but with
simple validation hooks.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

Params::Smart, IO::Prompt::Tiny.
Minimum Perl version is 5.6.2.
The test suite requires Capture::Tiny.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc IO::Prompt::Tiny

You can also look for information at:

    Github repo:
        http://www.github.com/daoswald/IO-Prompt-Hooked

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=IO-Prompt-Hooked

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/IO-Prompt-Hooked

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/IO-Prompt-Hooked

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/IO-Prompt-Hooked/


